  * Upload to unstable.
  * Add call to dh_desktop for mythtv-backend and mythtv-frontend packages.
  * Add two patches from Ubuntu :
      o 03_changeset_16483.patch Fixes DVD menu handling problem.
      o 04_changeset_16577.patch Fixes UPnP breakage on PS3.
  * Added more --enable options from Ubuntu TOP_SECRET_OPTS variable ;)
