mythtv (0.21-0.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release.
  * Removed 01_debian, 05_11372, 06_alsa_default, 08_mythtv-perl,
    09_scroll-wheel and 10_mythtv_alsa_non_mmap_fallback.2 patches.
  * Doesn't build with --enable-proc-opt but with --arch=i486 --cpu=i486
    --tune=i486 instead.

 -- Christian Marillat <marillat@debian.org>  Sun, 09 Mar 2008 11:55:19 +0100

